sequenceDiagram
    participant LLM as LLM Agent
    participant MCP as MCP Server
    participant APP as Application Services
    participant DOM as Domain
    participant INFRA as Infrastructure

    LLM->>MCP: tool_call(get_call_hierarchy)
    MCP->>APP: NavigationService
    APP->>DOM: Symbol lookup
    DOM->>INFRA: Parse source (Tree-sitter)
    INFRA-->>DOM: AST + Symbols
    DOM-->>APP: Call hierarchy
    APP-->>MCP: DTO response
    MCP-->>LLM: JSON result